00:11:13.350 --> 00:11:22.485 align:middle line:90%


00:11:22.485 --> 00:11:25.180 align:middle line:10%
We're talking to
Neale Donald Walsch

00:11:25.180 --> 00:11:30.220 align:middle line:10%
about the third volume of
"Conversations with God,"

00:11:30.220 --> 00:11:32.090 align:middle line:10%
an uncommon dialogue.

00:11:32.090 --> 00:11:32.890 align:middle line:90%
Welcome back.

00:11:32.890 --> 00:11:34.210 align:middle line:90%
>> Thank you.

00:11:34.210 --> 00:11:36.910 align:middle line:84%
>> We were talking about
manifesting anything you want

00:11:36.910 --> 00:11:40.060 align:middle line:84%
in your life, and
about how, at first,

00:11:40.060 --> 00:11:43.780 align:middle line:84%
of course we all know that
the idea must come first.

00:11:43.780 --> 00:11:46.060 align:middle line:84%
Henry Ford didn't
get the car going

00:11:46.060 --> 00:11:47.770 align:middle line:90%
until he had it in his mind.

00:11:47.770 --> 00:11:50.380 align:middle line:84%
>> That's right, but I want to
correct something, if I may.

00:11:50.380 --> 00:11:51.820 align:middle line:90%
It's more than just terminology.

00:11:51.820 --> 00:11:55.090 align:middle line:10%
The truth is God says, you may
not have anything you want.

00:11:55.090 --> 00:11:56.560 align:middle line:10%
And this is a
startling statement

00:11:56.560 --> 00:12:00.400 align:middle line:10%
that's made in the dialogue, you
may not have anything you want.

00:12:00.400 --> 00:12:02.290 align:middle line:84%
Because the very act
of wanting something

00:12:02.290 --> 00:12:05.860 align:middle line:84%
pushes it away from you,
because if you are expressing

00:12:05.860 --> 00:12:08.920 align:middle line:84%
a wantingness for something,
that's a statement

00:12:08.920 --> 00:12:11.410 align:middle line:90%
that you do not now have it.

00:12:11.410 --> 00:12:15.110 align:middle line:84%
And as you believe it,
so will it be with you.

00:12:15.110 --> 00:12:18.428 align:middle line:84%
Therefore, if you're sitting in
a pool of desire for something,

00:12:18.428 --> 00:12:20.470 align:middle line:84%
then you're as much as
announcing to the universe

00:12:20.470 --> 00:12:22.463 align:middle line:84%
that it's not there
right then and there.

00:12:22.463 --> 00:12:24.130 align:middle line:84%
And that, of course,
makes it impossible

00:12:24.130 --> 00:12:28.120 align:middle line:84%
for you to experience it in
your life, for your reality is

00:12:28.120 --> 00:12:31.540 align:middle line:84%
created by your thought about
it, and by the word you speak

00:12:31.540 --> 00:12:33.423 align:middle line:84%
and the actions
that you undertake.

00:12:33.423 --> 00:12:34.840 align:middle line:84%
Therefore, the
first thing we have

00:12:34.840 --> 00:12:37.930 align:middle line:84%
to eliminate from our mind in
the process of manifestation

00:12:37.930 --> 00:12:41.050 align:middle line:84%
is we have to eliminate any
thought that we do not now

00:12:41.050 --> 00:12:43.270 align:middle line:84%
have, or, in the
words of some people,

00:12:43.270 --> 00:12:44.740 align:middle line:84%
that we somehow
can't have, there's

00:12:44.740 --> 00:12:46.660 align:middle line:84%
some reason why
we can't have what

00:12:46.660 --> 00:12:51.400 align:middle line:84%
it is we choose to experience
in life, but rather to say,

00:12:51.400 --> 00:12:53.680 align:middle line:84%
with all the faith
we can muster,

00:12:53.680 --> 00:12:58.000 align:middle line:84%
not only can I have that,
I have that right now.

00:12:58.000 --> 00:12:59.590 align:middle line:84%
To really believe
the highest promise

00:12:59.590 --> 00:13:04.720 align:middle line:84%
of God, which is, even before
you ask, I will have answered.

00:13:04.720 --> 00:13:07.000 align:middle line:84%
So people of
enormous faith never

00:13:07.000 --> 00:13:11.680 align:middle line:84%
say I want, but rather
they say, all the good,

00:13:11.680 --> 00:13:14.660 align:middle line:84%
all the compassion, all
the help, all the money,

00:13:14.660 --> 00:13:16.420 align:middle line:84%
all the love, all
the health that I

00:13:16.420 --> 00:13:18.940 align:middle line:90%
choose is coming to me now.

00:13:18.940 --> 00:13:22.920 align:middle line:84%
One of the greatest prayers
I ever heard goes like this.

00:13:22.920 --> 00:13:27.160 align:middle line:84%
"Help me to understand, dear
God, that this problem has

00:13:27.160 --> 00:13:29.290 align:middle line:90%
already been solved for me."

00:13:29.290 --> 00:13:33.700 align:middle line:84%
That this problem has
already been solved for me.

00:13:33.700 --> 00:13:36.730 align:middle line:84%
And one of the more startling
examples of that in my life

00:13:36.730 --> 00:13:39.100 align:middle line:84%
was when I needed a great
deal of money at one point.

00:13:39.100 --> 00:13:40.933 align:middle line:84%
And I had some people
who were upset with me

00:13:40.933 --> 00:13:42.850 align:middle line:84%
and wanted that money
by a certain date.

00:13:42.850 --> 00:13:43.930 align:middle line:84%
And I owed it to
them, and I really

00:13:43.930 --> 00:13:45.610 align:middle line:84%
needed to get it for them,
and I didn't have it.

00:13:45.610 --> 00:13:47.950 align:middle line:84%
And I did everything I could
think of, Corrine, for it,

00:13:47.950 --> 00:13:49.900 align:middle line:84%
days and days and days,
for several weeks, trying

00:13:49.900 --> 00:13:51.067 align:middle line:90%
to pull together that money.

00:13:51.067 --> 00:13:52.200 align:middle line:90%
It was a large sum.

00:13:52.200 --> 00:13:53.950 align:middle line:84%
I called my father, I
called some friends,

00:13:53.950 --> 00:13:56.260 align:middle line:84%
I called in all the
chips I had out there,

00:13:56.260 --> 00:13:57.640 align:middle line:90%
and I couldn't get it together.

00:13:57.640 --> 00:13:58.480 align:middle line:90%
Not all of it.

00:13:58.480 --> 00:14:00.060 align:middle line:84%
In fact, only about
a third of it.

00:14:00.060 --> 00:14:02.602 align:middle line:84%
And now had come the day that
I needed to deliver this money.

00:14:02.602 --> 00:14:04.810 align:middle line:84%
And I said to God, all right,
well, whatever you say.

00:14:04.810 --> 00:14:06.310 align:middle line:90%
I'm leaving it up to you now.

00:14:06.310 --> 00:14:08.268 align:middle line:84%
I did what I should have
done at the beginning.

00:14:08.268 --> 00:14:09.370 align:middle line:90%
I let go and let God.

00:14:09.370 --> 00:14:11.020 align:middle line:84%
And I said, OK, God,
whatever you want,

00:14:11.020 --> 00:14:13.660 align:middle line:84%
because I can't
solve this by myself.

00:14:13.660 --> 00:14:16.112 align:middle line:84%
And the next day, I went
to the post office box,

00:14:16.112 --> 00:14:18.070 align:middle line:84%
just doing my normal
routine, everyday things--

00:14:18.070 --> 00:14:18.960 align:middle line:90%
it was a Monday--

00:14:18.960 --> 00:14:21.460 align:middle line:84%
and I found an envelope in there
that had been sitting there

00:14:21.460 --> 00:14:23.260 align:middle line:90%
since the Friday before.

00:14:23.260 --> 00:14:25.690 align:middle line:84%
Three days of worrying, and
there was an envelope sitting

00:14:25.690 --> 00:14:28.420 align:middle line:84%
there since Friday with a
check from some guy in Florida

00:14:28.420 --> 00:14:30.690 align:middle line:84%
who owed me some money for
many years, and he said,

00:14:30.690 --> 00:14:33.190 align:middle line:84%
you know it's been bothering
me, and I'm way behind on this,

00:14:33.190 --> 00:14:34.330 align:middle line:84%
but I hope you'll
accept this, I hope

00:14:34.330 --> 00:14:36.280 align:middle line:84%
you don't mind that
it's several years late.

00:14:36.280 --> 00:14:37.300 align:middle line:90%
Mind?

00:14:37.300 --> 00:14:39.470 align:middle line:84%
It was the miracle
of the year for me.

00:14:39.470 --> 00:14:43.900 align:middle line:84%
But what I learned from that
was, even before I asked,

00:14:43.900 --> 00:14:44.980 align:middle line:90%
God had already answered.

00:14:44.980 --> 00:14:47.230 align:middle line:84%
I could see God up there
saying, Neale, just

00:14:47.230 --> 00:14:49.270 align:middle line:90%
go to the post office box.

00:14:49.270 --> 00:14:51.310 align:middle line:90%
It's already there.

00:14:51.310 --> 00:14:53.560 align:middle line:84%
Well, that's a very striking
example of something that

00:14:53.560 --> 00:14:55.270 align:middle line:90%
happens in many people's lives.

00:14:55.270 --> 00:14:59.140 align:middle line:84%
Sometimes in a more subtle way,
but it happens nonetheless.

00:14:59.140 --> 00:15:02.050 align:middle line:84%
Often, people discover, if
they can accept the good that's

00:15:02.050 --> 00:15:04.750 align:middle line:84%
coming to them, that in fact,
it's not only coming to them,

00:15:04.750 --> 00:15:06.250 align:middle line:90%
it's been there all along.

00:15:06.250 --> 00:15:08.080 align:middle line:84%
They simply haven't
been able to see it

00:15:08.080 --> 00:15:10.450 align:middle line:90%
for all of their disbelief.

00:15:10.450 --> 00:15:13.060 align:middle line:84%
>> But does that manifest in
regular, practical matters,

00:15:13.060 --> 00:15:17.410 align:middle line:84%
such as suppose I've
always wanted a red Jaguar.

00:15:17.410 --> 00:15:18.767 align:middle line:90%
I mean, can I have that?

00:15:18.767 --> 00:15:21.100 align:middle line:84%
>> You can, if that's your
highest thought about what it

00:15:21.100 --> 00:15:23.890 align:middle line:84%
is you would choose to
experience in your life.

00:15:23.890 --> 00:15:25.840 align:middle line:84%
Yes, you can experience
a red Jaguar.

00:15:25.840 --> 00:15:28.310 align:middle line:84%
>> But you cannot doubt that
you are going to get it.

00:15:28.310 --> 00:15:28.720 align:middle line:90%
>> No.

00:15:28.720 --> 00:15:29.610 align:middle line:90%
>> That's the big thing.

00:15:29.610 --> 00:15:30.735 align:middle line:90%
>> These are not new ideas.

00:15:30.735 --> 00:15:32.770 align:middle line:84%
Norman Vincent Peale
wrote 45 years ago,

00:15:32.770 --> 00:15:35.320 align:middle line:84%
if you want a red Jaguar,
just think about a red Jaguar,

00:15:35.320 --> 00:15:38.092 align:middle line:84%
and sooner or later, depending
on the amount of faith

00:15:38.092 --> 00:15:39.550 align:middle line:84%
and energy you put
behind that, you

00:15:39.550 --> 00:15:41.290 align:middle line:84%
will, in fact, have
that red Jaguar.

00:15:41.290 --> 00:15:44.410 align:middle line:84%
The power of positive
thinking is not a new thought.

00:15:44.410 --> 00:15:47.260 align:middle line:84%
It's been around, that
whole idea, for a long time.

00:15:47.260 --> 00:15:49.750 align:middle line:84%
But the real central question
is, why would a person

00:15:49.750 --> 00:15:52.120 align:middle line:84%
choose a red Jaguar out
of all the things in life

00:15:52.120 --> 00:15:53.200 align:middle line:90%
one would choose to have?

00:15:53.200 --> 00:15:54.380 align:middle line:90%
How about this one?

00:15:54.380 --> 00:15:58.450 align:middle line:84%
How about I choose to learn,
I choose to experience,

00:15:58.450 --> 00:16:01.270 align:middle line:84%
I choose to know myself as
the highest level of love

00:16:01.270 --> 00:16:02.855 align:middle line:90%
I could ever imagine.

00:16:02.855 --> 00:16:05.230 align:middle line:84%
I choose to touch people's
lives in a way that heals them

00:16:05.230 --> 00:16:08.590 align:middle line:84%
forever, that alters their
very experience of themselves

00:16:08.590 --> 00:16:10.570 align:middle line:84%
and that gives them
back to themselves.

00:16:10.570 --> 00:16:14.080 align:middle line:84%
I choose peace in my
life and for this planet.

00:16:14.080 --> 00:16:15.960 align:middle line:84%
I'll take that over
a red Jaguar anytime.

00:16:15.960 --> 00:16:17.560 align:middle line:84%
And there are people
now on the planet

00:16:17.560 --> 00:16:20.240 align:middle line:84%
who are making those
kinds of choices.

00:16:20.240 --> 00:16:23.910 align:middle line:84%
>> Well, the reason we want the
red Jaguar is because we think

00:16:23.910 --> 00:16:25.118 align:middle line:90%
it is going to give us peace.

00:16:25.118 --> 00:16:25.918 align:middle line:90%
>> Of course.

00:16:25.918 --> 00:16:26.760 align:middle line:90%
And happiness.

00:16:26.760 --> 00:16:29.850 align:middle line:84%
>> So that you're
skipping over the Jaguar,

00:16:29.850 --> 00:16:31.230 align:middle line:90%
going right to the peace.

00:16:31.230 --> 00:16:34.350 align:middle line:84%
But I think the most
important point here

00:16:34.350 --> 00:16:39.510 align:middle line:84%
is, now, when you start taking
this whole reality of being

00:16:39.510 --> 00:16:43.800 align:middle line:84%
able to create what
you really desire,

00:16:43.800 --> 00:16:47.430 align:middle line:84%
and go into your chapter
here where you talk about

00:16:47.430 --> 00:16:51.180 align:middle line:84%
and ask God what
happens when we die.

00:16:51.180 --> 00:16:53.430 align:middle line:84%
>> Well, that's the most
profound question, of course,

00:16:53.430 --> 00:16:56.010 align:middle line:84%
in the universe, and it was
the most important question

00:16:56.010 --> 00:16:57.660 align:middle line:90%
in the whole trilogy for me.

00:16:57.660 --> 00:17:01.140 align:middle line:84%
And God said, even as it is
in life, so is it in death,

00:17:01.140 --> 00:17:02.350 align:middle line:90%
or what you call death.

00:17:02.350 --> 00:17:04.392 align:middle line:84%
The first thing we have
to understand, of course,

00:17:04.392 --> 00:17:06.540 align:middle line:84%
is that death as we
understand it does not exist.

00:17:06.540 --> 00:17:08.498 align:middle line:84%
But if we can get past
those terms for a minute

00:17:08.498 --> 00:17:11.880 align:middle line:84%
and just use them loosely,
after the thing we call death,

00:17:11.880 --> 00:17:14.550 align:middle line:84%
God says, you will
experience yourself exactly

00:17:14.550 --> 00:17:15.750 align:middle line:90%
as you do in life.

00:17:15.750 --> 00:17:19.589 align:middle line:84%
That is, as a being capable
of experiencing whatever

00:17:19.589 --> 00:17:21.198 align:middle line:90%
it is that you call forth.

00:17:21.198 --> 00:17:22.740 align:middle line:84%
Only the speed with
which you produce

00:17:22.740 --> 00:17:25.650 align:middle line:84%
results will be instantaneous,
whereas in this lifetime,

00:17:25.650 --> 00:17:28.530 align:middle line:84%
because of the slow process
of the illusion that we have

00:17:28.530 --> 00:17:31.740 align:middle line:84%
created called time,
it may be a little bit

00:17:31.740 --> 00:17:35.328 align:middle line:84%
between our thought about it and
the experience of it, whereas--

00:17:35.328 --> 00:17:36.870 align:middle line:84%
I'm going to use
another loose term--

00:17:36.870 --> 00:17:40.140 align:middle line:84%
on the other side of life,
in that place that we call

00:17:40.140 --> 00:17:43.020 align:middle line:84%
the after-death experience,
immediately when

00:17:43.020 --> 00:17:45.240 align:middle line:84%
you think of a thing,
that which you choose

00:17:45.240 --> 00:17:46.980 align:middle line:84%
to experience
through that thought

00:17:46.980 --> 00:17:48.610 align:middle line:90%
is brought into your reality.

00:17:48.610 --> 00:17:50.340 align:middle line:84%
So the results
are instantaneous,

00:17:50.340 --> 00:17:51.405 align:middle line:90%
and they're immediate.

00:17:51.405 --> 00:17:53.280 align:middle line:84%
And that's when we really
have an opportunity

00:17:53.280 --> 00:17:55.940 align:middle line:84%
to experience and to
express who we really are.

00:17:55.940 --> 00:17:59.495 align:middle line:84%
An instant creator of whatever
reality we would select.

00:17:59.495 --> 00:18:00.870 align:middle line:84%
That's what heaven
is, of course,

00:18:00.870 --> 00:18:04.680 align:middle line:84%
being able to have whatever
you want right then and there.

00:18:04.680 --> 00:18:06.310 align:middle line:90%
>> I love the paragraph--

00:18:06.310 --> 00:18:08.520 align:middle line:84%
>> I just caught myself
in a verbal contradiction,

00:18:08.520 --> 00:18:10.770 align:middle line:84%
but it's being able to have
whatever you choose right then

00:18:10.770 --> 00:18:11.570 align:middle line:90%
and there.

00:18:11.570 --> 00:18:14.430 align:middle line:84%
For in the afterlife, as in
this life, if we want it,

00:18:14.430 --> 00:18:16.393 align:middle line:90%
we're saying we don't have it.

00:18:16.393 --> 00:18:18.810 align:middle line:84%
>> So the big difference that
you're making in the book is

00:18:18.810 --> 00:18:22.000 align:middle line:84%
that, in this so-called
physical world--

00:18:22.000 --> 00:18:22.800 align:middle line:90%
>> Yes.

00:18:22.800 --> 00:18:24.750 align:middle line:84%
>> --sometimes, there
is a time lapse.

00:18:24.750 --> 00:18:24.970 align:middle line:90%
>> Yes.

00:18:24.970 --> 00:18:26.873 align:middle line:84%
>> And as soon as you
reach the other side,

00:18:26.873 --> 00:18:27.790 align:middle line:90%
there's no time lapse.

00:18:27.790 --> 00:18:32.010 align:middle line:84%
And I love the way God
describes the confusion.

00:18:32.010 --> 00:18:32.880 align:middle line:90%
Tell us about that.

00:18:32.880 --> 00:18:35.247 align:middle line:84%
>> Well, people, when they've
moved into the afterlife,

00:18:35.247 --> 00:18:37.830 align:middle line:84%
often they don't even know that
they're the thing that we call

00:18:37.830 --> 00:18:40.080 align:middle line:84%
dead, because, of
course, they're not dead.

00:18:40.080 --> 00:18:41.760 align:middle line:90%
They're very much alive.

00:18:41.760 --> 00:18:45.060 align:middle line:84%
And they expected to be
dead, and they're not dead,

00:18:45.060 --> 00:18:47.370 align:middle line:84%
so they move into an
experience that looks and feels

00:18:47.370 --> 00:18:50.197 align:middle line:84%
and is experienced in
a whole different way

00:18:50.197 --> 00:18:52.530 align:middle line:84%
than they might have imagined
that they would experience

00:18:52.530 --> 00:18:55.270 align:middle line:84%
death if they had any
thought about it at all.

00:18:55.270 --> 00:18:57.450 align:middle line:84%
So here they are,
simply feeling exactly

00:18:57.450 --> 00:18:59.940 align:middle line:84%
as they felt a moment ago,
except they may notice,

00:18:59.940 --> 00:19:02.340 align:middle line:84%
oh my goodness, my body is
down there, and here I am.

00:19:02.340 --> 00:19:03.760 align:middle line:84%
I'm feeling exactly
the same way,

00:19:03.760 --> 00:19:05.580 align:middle line:84%
but there I am, and I'm not
over there, I'm over here,

00:19:05.580 --> 00:19:06.997 align:middle line:84%
and what is all
this about anyway.

00:19:06.997 --> 00:19:09.540 align:middle line:84%
So there's a great
deal of confusion.

00:19:09.540 --> 00:19:11.300 align:middle line:84%
But then, after
that confusion is--

00:19:11.300 --> 00:19:15.150 align:middle line:84%
and we're normally
sent guides and, I

00:19:15.150 --> 00:19:18.300 align:middle line:84%
want to say, angels or
helpers or other souls,

00:19:18.300 --> 00:19:21.900 align:middle line:84%
really, who will fly to
us at that moment, maybe

00:19:21.900 --> 00:19:25.260 align:middle line:84%
those who have passed before
that we are very fond of

00:19:25.260 --> 00:19:26.370 align:middle line:90%
or we've loved very much.

00:19:26.370 --> 00:19:28.470 align:middle line:84%
Perhaps our parents or
whoever will show up

00:19:28.470 --> 00:19:32.550 align:middle line:84%
at that time to help
us and say, Neale,

00:19:32.550 --> 00:19:35.850 align:middle line:84%
this is what's happening now,
and here's where you are.

00:19:35.850 --> 00:19:37.675 align:middle line:84%
And then we begin to
experience the joy.

00:19:37.675 --> 00:19:40.050 align:middle line:84%
We begin to notice that whatever
we're thinking, wherever

00:19:40.050 --> 00:19:42.210 align:middle line:84%
we want to go with the
speed of our thought

00:19:42.210 --> 00:19:44.730 align:middle line:90%
is created in our reality.

00:19:44.730 --> 00:19:48.547 align:middle line:84%
But even as glorious as
that experience may feel,

00:19:48.547 --> 00:19:50.130 align:middle line:84%
after a while, it's
simply not enough.

00:19:50.130 --> 00:19:52.150 align:middle line:84%
It could be actually boring,
if you could think about it.

00:19:52.150 --> 00:19:54.500 align:middle line:84%
If you could have whatever
you wanted instantaneously,

00:19:54.500 --> 00:19:55.958 align:middle line:84%
a very few moments
of that, and you

00:19:55.958 --> 00:19:57.990 align:middle line:84%
might start thinking
about larger challenges.

00:19:57.990 --> 00:19:58.790 align:middle line:90%
>> Try me.

00:19:58.790 --> 00:20:00.422 align:middle line:90%
[LAUGHTER]

00:20:00.422 --> 00:20:01.420 align:middle line:90%


00:20:01.420 --> 00:20:04.140 align:middle line:84%
>> You'd be you'd be surprised
how one would say, you know,

00:20:04.140 --> 00:20:07.170 align:middle line:84%
this is all a lot of fun, but
I think I want to go back there

00:20:07.170 --> 00:20:10.770 align:middle line:84%
and try that again and do it
another way and experience

00:20:10.770 --> 00:20:13.290 align:middle line:84%
myself at the next
highest level.

00:20:13.290 --> 00:20:15.090 align:middle line:84%
Even in this lifetime,
when we have it

00:20:15.090 --> 00:20:17.820 align:middle line:84%
all solved, and there are
no more problems and nothing

00:20:17.820 --> 00:20:20.640 align:middle line:84%
more to conquer,
the natural tendency

00:20:20.640 --> 00:20:24.930 align:middle line:84%
of truly wonderful and
enlightened human beings

00:20:24.930 --> 00:20:26.670 align:middle line:90%
is to seek a newer challenge.

00:20:26.670 --> 00:20:28.890 align:middle line:84%
We're never tired of
climbing the mountain.

00:20:28.890 --> 00:20:32.290 align:middle line:84%
In truth, we say we want it all
to end and all to be smooth,

00:20:32.290 --> 00:20:34.440 align:middle line:84%
but the truth is, for
every truly great explorer

00:20:34.440 --> 00:20:37.140 align:middle line:84%
and every wonderful mind on the
planet, when the game is over,

00:20:37.140 --> 00:20:39.090 align:middle line:84%
they start a new
one immediately.

00:20:39.090 --> 00:20:41.220 align:middle line:84%
No one wants to get to
the top of the mountain.

00:20:41.220 --> 00:20:41.470 align:middle line:90%
At least--

00:20:41.470 --> 00:20:42.060 align:middle line:90%
>> That's no fun.

00:20:42.060 --> 00:20:43.710 align:middle line:84%
>> --at least, they
don't want to stay there.

00:20:43.710 --> 00:20:44.700 align:middle line:84%
Once you're on the
top of the mountain,

00:20:44.700 --> 00:20:46.075 align:middle line:84%
you start looking
around, where's

00:20:46.075 --> 00:20:47.540 align:middle line:90%
the next mountain to climb?

00:20:47.540 --> 00:20:49.800 align:middle line:84%
>> One of the things that I
thought was so interesting

00:20:49.800 --> 00:20:52.170 align:middle line:84%
about that chapter on death
is that so many people go

00:20:52.170 --> 00:20:56.220 align:middle line:84%
to psychics to contact
the souls of the departed.

00:20:56.220 --> 00:20:57.020 align:middle line:90%
>> Yes.

00:20:57.020 --> 00:20:58.290 align:middle line:90%
And they don't have to.

00:20:58.290 --> 00:21:01.110 align:middle line:84%
You can contact the souls of
the departed in an instant.

00:21:01.110 --> 00:21:04.560 align:middle line:84%
You cannot have a thought about
a dearly departed loved one

00:21:04.560 --> 00:21:07.740 align:middle line:84%
without the essence of that
person coming flying right

00:21:07.740 --> 00:21:10.680 align:middle line:84%
to you and being right there
alongside of you as part

00:21:10.680 --> 00:21:11.910 align:middle line:90%
of your experience.

00:21:11.910 --> 00:21:14.700 align:middle line:84%
It's like sending out a
telegram, be here now.

00:21:14.700 --> 00:21:17.580 align:middle line:84%
And so you don't need
a medium or a psychic

00:21:17.580 --> 00:21:20.990 align:middle line:84%
to contact anyone
from the other side.

00:21:20.990 --> 00:21:24.340 align:middle line:10%
Your very thought about them--
you know the best medium?

00:21:24.340 --> 00:21:28.120 align:middle line:10%
Love is the best medium
of communication.

00:21:28.120 --> 00:21:30.390 align:middle line:84%
All you have to do is
think of another person,

00:21:30.390 --> 00:21:34.540 align:middle line:84%
one who has gone before, from a
place of deep and abiding love.

00:21:34.540 --> 00:21:37.210 align:middle line:84%
And that love sent out is
received by the essence,

00:21:37.210 --> 00:21:38.530 align:middle line:90%
the soul of that person.

00:21:38.530 --> 00:21:40.150 align:middle line:90%
And they're right there.

00:21:40.150 --> 00:21:42.010 align:middle line:90%
They can hear your every word.

00:21:42.010 --> 00:21:45.610 align:middle line:84%
If you listen really
carefully, you'll

00:21:45.610 --> 00:21:47.410 align:middle line:84%
be able to hear
their words, as well.

00:21:47.410 --> 00:21:50.430 align:middle line:90%


00:21:50.430 --> 00:21:53.380 align:middle line:84%
>> Well, there are a lot of
people out there who will get

00:21:53.380 --> 00:21:56.325 align:middle line:84%
a great deal of consolation
from that statement.

00:21:56.325 --> 00:21:58.575 align:middle line:84%
>> Because it's true, and
truth is a great consolation

00:21:58.575 --> 00:21:59.140 align:middle line:90%
in the face--

00:21:59.140 --> 00:21:59.530 align:middle line:90%
>> And one of the things--

00:21:59.530 --> 00:22:00.405 align:middle line:90%
>> --of all the lies.

00:22:00.405 --> 00:22:03.250 align:middle line:84%
>> --you say in the book
is that, many times,

00:22:03.250 --> 00:22:05.380 align:middle line:84%
the souls of the
departed contact us,

00:22:05.380 --> 00:22:06.980 align:middle line:90%
but we don't believe it.

00:22:06.980 --> 00:22:07.780 align:middle line:90%
>> Yes.

00:22:07.780 --> 00:22:09.160 align:middle line:90%
>> We don't believe it.

00:22:09.160 --> 00:22:11.500 align:middle line:84%
I wish we could go on with
this for another two hours,

00:22:11.500 --> 00:22:13.830 align:middle line:84%
but they're giving me a
signal that we're through.

00:22:13.830 --> 00:22:17.740 align:middle line:84%
This has been a fascinating,
fascinating conversation.

00:22:17.740 --> 00:22:19.570 align:middle line:84%
We've been talking to
Neale Donald Walsch

00:22:19.570 --> 00:22:23.170 align:middle line:84%
here, who is the
author of all three

00:22:23.170 --> 00:22:28.600 align:middle line:84%
of the books called
"Conversations with God."

00:22:28.600 --> 00:22:32.770 align:middle line:84%
Personally, it's my favorite
of three, book three.

00:22:32.770 --> 00:22:34.210 align:middle line:90%
I loved it.

00:22:34.210 --> 00:22:37.690 align:middle line:84%
I think that you will benefit
a great deal when you read it.

00:22:37.690 --> 00:22:39.760 align:middle line:84%
And as I always tell
you around here,

00:22:39.760 --> 00:22:42.790 align:middle line:84%
we bring you miracles
on this show.

00:22:42.790 --> 00:22:43.990 align:middle line:90%
Keep coming back.

